OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780938366
OL,3,CFirst underwater footage of adult
OL,4,Cgreat white shark recorded in
OL,5,CMediterranean
OL,7,FThe great white shark came face to
OL,8,Fface with the divers
OL,10,FA great white shark has been spotted
OL,11,Funderwater in the Mediterranean Sea
OL,12,Ffor the very first time, new footage
OL,13,Fshows.
OL,15,FDerek Remmers, a conservation diver,
OL,16,Fspotted the rare shark during a
OL,17,Fmission to recover abandoned fishing
OL,18,Fnets from a shipwreck in the Strait of
OL,19,FSicily between the Italian island and
OL,20,FTunisia last month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780938366
OL,3,CFirst underwater footage of adult
OL,4,Cgreat white shark recorded in
OL,5,CMediterranean
OL,7,FMarine experts have said it's highly
OL,8,Funusual for great white sharks to be
OL,9,Fspotted in the Mediterranean, and the
OL,10,Ffootage is an important record for
OL,11,Fscientists.
OL,13,FSpeaking of the encounter, Remmers
OL,14,Fsaid, "Statistically, it is way more
OL,15,Flikely to win the lotto jackpot than
OL,16,Fto meet such an iconic animal
OL,17,Funderwater.
OL,19,F"You spend decades diving wrecks and
OL,20,Fremoving ghost nets, but nothing
OL,21,Fprepares you for a moment like this.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
