PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780938366
OL,3,CFirst underwater footage of adult
OL,4,Cgreat white shark recorded in
OL,5,CMediterranean
OL,7,F"An offshore underwater shark
OL,8,Fencounter in the Mediterranean is
OL,9,Finsane."
OL,11,FDr Carlo Cattano, a researcher at the
OL,12,FSicily Marine Centre who is
OL,13,Fcollaborating with the mission to
OL,14,Fremove old nets in the area, said:
OL,15,F"Most of our knowledge on the White
OL,16,FSharks in the Mediterranean Sea comes
OL,17,Ffrom records of dead specimens caught
OL,18,Fby fishing operations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
