FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780938366
OL,3,CFirst underwater footage of adult
OL,4,Cgreat white shark recorded in
OL,5,CMediterranean
OL,7,F"Observations like this are extremely
OL,8,Fvaluable for improving our
OL,9,Funderstanding of the distribution,
OL,10,Fhabits, and behaviour of this
OL,11,Fcritically endangered species, whose
OL,12,Fsurvival is threatened by human
OL,13,Factivities."
OL,15,FThere have been occasional surface
OL,16,Fsightings of great white sharks in the
OL,17,FMediterranean Sea, but this is
OL,18,Fbelieved to be the first time an adult
OL,19,Fgreat white shark has been recorded
OL,20,Funderwater.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
