OL,3,CFirst underwater footage of adult
OL,4,Cgreat white shark recorded in
OL,5,CMediterranean
OL,7,FGreat white sharks are more commonly
OL,8,Ffound off the coast of South Africa
OL,9,Fand Australia.
OL,11,FThe Strait of Sicily represents both a
OL,12,Fcrucial biodiversity hotspot and one
OL,13,Fof the Mediterranean's most
OL,14,Fintensively fished zones.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
